OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FA health charity in is urging people
OL,8,Fto take steps to reduce trigger
OL,9,Fsymptoms of asthma that could lead to
OL,10,Fan asthma attack.
OL,12,FThis World Asthma Day (May 7)
OL,13,Fsufferers of asthma are being urged to
OL,14,Fknow what triggers their condition by
OL,15,FAsthma and Lung UK Cymru.
OL,17,FThe charity said "it will help reduce
OL,18,Fsymptoms and prevent attacks."
