OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FNew research also showed the largest
OL,8,Ftrigger for s to be a cold or flu, or
OL,9,Fchanges in the weather.
OL,11,FHighlighting the impact that triggers
OL,12,Fhave had on her asthma, Lisa Hall, a
OL,13,Fbiomedical scientist from Newport said
OL,14,Fshe struggles with her breathing daily
OL,15,Fand has many asthma triggers including
OL,16,Fcleaning products, hot weather and
OL,17,Fpollen.
OL,19,FMs Hall was diagnosed with severe
OL,20,Fasthma when she was 28 years old.
