OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FStruggling with her breathing daily,
OL,8,Fshe has lost count of the amount of
OL,9,Ftimes she has ended up in hospital.
OL,11,FShe said: "I had my first big attack
OL,12,Fwhen I was 29 years old and I was in
OL,13,Fhospital for ten days. Everything kind
OL,14,Fof settled down over the next few
OL,15,Fmonths until June 2018 when it went
OL,16,Fbadly wrong and it has stayed like
OL,17,Fthat since.
OL,19,F"The 13th of March (this year) was my
OL,20,Flast one and the ambulance control
OL,21,Fsent the air ambulance out to me."
