OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"My asthma is very unpredictable, and
OL,8,FI have lost count of how many times I
OL,9,Fhave been hospitalised. Things are
OL,10,Ffrustrating at times, but you've got
OL,11,Fno choice but to carry on working
OL,12,Fthings through."
OL,14,FMs Hall expressed that she has many
OL,15,Ftriggers, but said one of the worst is
OL,16,Fwhen people spray perfume or deodorant
OL,17,Fpublicly as she finds it "really
OL,18,Fdifficult."
