OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FShe added that heat, humidity and
OL,8,Fpollen are also common factors which
OL,9,Faffect her breathing.
OL,11,F"If I step into somewhere that's
OL,12,Freally humid, that's pretty much
OL,13,Falmost instant , I just get tight and
OL,14,Fwheezy, have a cough and then it just
OL,15,Fgets worse and worse until I stop
OL,16,Fmoving air."
