OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FShe continued: "It's very challenging
OL,8,Fand affects my day-to-day life. I have
OL,9,Fto be aware of my environment as
OL,10,Fsudden changes in the weather or
OL,11,Fbreathing in cleaning products and
OL,12,Fsmells such as perfume and air
OL,13,Ffresheners can leave me struggling to
OL,14,Fbreathe.
OL,16,F"I breathe better inside than out. I
OL,17,Fam a biomedical scientist and am very
OL,18,Flucky I work in a climate-controlled
OL,19,Flab, especially in the summer months
OL,20,Fwhen hot weather and pollen are
OL,21,Fdangerous for me."
