OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,FThe charity spoke to 513 people with
OL,8,Fasthma in Wales and their survey
OL,9,Frevealed that:
OL,11,FHe said: "This World Asthma Day, we
OL,12,Fwant to encourage the 314,000 people
OL,13,Fwith asthma in Wales to look after
OL,14,Ftheir lung health by being aware of
OL,15,Ftheir triggers, getting an asthma
OL,16,Faction plan so they know what to do if
OL,17,Ftheir symptoms worsen, and having
OL,18,Ftheir medication and inhaler technique
OL,19,Fregularly reviewed by their GP or
OL,20,Fnurse.
