OL,3,C'Unpredictable' asthma triggers cause
OL,4,Cwoman to be hospitalised 'countless'
OL,5,Ctimes
OL,7,F"Triggers can be unpredictable and
OL,8,Fvariable, and you should never be
OL,9,Fcomplacent about them.
OL,11,FHe added: "Asthma triggers can be
OL,12,Fdifficult to navigate, and some, such
OL,13,Fas the weather and viral infections,
OL,14,Fare impossible to avoid.
OL,16,F"But if it's managed properly, being
OL,17,Fexposed to a trigger should not be
OL,18,Flife-threatening."
